{
  "stem": "25589.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even us, even the people outside-- there were people starving from-- from-- from-- from hunger.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans took it all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whatever food there was, they-- they cleaned the wholesales out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, I would always have plenty to eat-- vegetables.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The vegetables were still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the potatoes were still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everything was still there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they haul it away in trucks-- truckloads, to feed their-- to feed their army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They couldn't care less if we lived or died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That could be Jews, or it could be-- there was no Jews, as far as they were concerned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was no Jews, so it was Gentile people that died.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, they picked the-- the Gentile people up to go to work in the concentration just as much as they did the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They didn't care, especially at the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They didn't care who they took.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They took children and old men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On my mother's side-- 1, 2. 3 brothers gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One had three children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on my father's side, three brothers-- four-- eight children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two children are still alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're living in Toronto-- on my mother's side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SIGHS] But the rest has all gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never heard from them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the people that came back, came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But most-- there's not too many people that came back from concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From there, they were like my-- my-- the same as my age.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, the people that went to concentration camps, you could say goodbye to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say-- I would say-- maybe 10% came back, out of the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's terrible to say, because they would have been all my age, and they would be married with children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there were a lot of grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
